data.description: This 1930s bungalow is more than just a house; it's a piece of history waiting to be embraced by a new generation of homeowners. As the original Homestead for the surrounding acreage, this home has been loved for generations. With its timeless elegance, modern comforts like a sunroom, exterior sprinkler system, rear patio deck with brand new built-in Calspa hot tub, Smart appliances, washer, dryer and the delightful bonus of a greenhouse (w/ electricity and plumbing) and workshop (w/ electricity) Newly installed HVAC heating system with Central air A/C including a 10yr transferable warranty. Additional renovations and updates being done currently, including new flooring with updated photos to soon follow. This home offers an idyllic retreat from the bustling world outside, don't miss your chance to make cherished memories in this captivating abode!
